lyrics:
[verse]
I wake up to sunlight, embracing the day
Grateful for blessings that come my way
In this world of chaos, I find my peace
Expressing gratitude, my soul finds release

[chorus]
Gratitude, my melody of truth
I sing with gratitude from the heart of my youth
With each breath I take, I'm thankful for all
Gratitude, my song, as I stand tall
